french far @-@ leave killer leave jail
ensisheim , france , april 14 , 2010 ( afp ) -
a former militant of the french far @-@ leave group action directe , georges cipriani , leave prison on parole on wednesday after 23 year behind bar for two high @-@ profile murder .
a policeman at the scene confirm to afp the identity of cipriani , 59 , who leave the prison in ensisheim in northeastern france wear a leather jacket and with long white hair .
cipriani be one of four member of action directe sentence to life in prison for the murder of renault chief george besse in 1986 and the head of government arm sale rene audran a year earlier .
the four include two women , joelle aubron who die of lung cancer in 2006 and nathalie menignon , who be parole in 2008 .
a fourth member , jean @-@ marc rouillan , remain behind bar .
cipriani leave ensisheim in a police vehicle bound for an open prison near strasbourg where the police officer say he be due to do community service include work at a food bank as part of his parole .
china president urge child safety after school killings
beijing , june 1 , 2010 ( afp ) -
chinese president hu jintao have call on the entire nation to do more to ensure the safety of children , state press say tuesday , in comment that follow a spate of grisly school killings .
" the entire society must pay importance to the safety of children and do everything to safeguard our motherland 's next generation , " the people 's daily quote hu as say .
hu be speak monday as he tour a beijing exhibit on transport and build safety with a group of schoolchildren on the eve of international children 's day , the report say .
his remark come after a spate of bloody school attack around china since late march which have leave 17 people dead , include 15 student , and score injure .
expert say the senseless assault reveal a china struggle to come to grip with rapid social change follow decade of boom economic growth .
on sunday , a 47 @-@ year @-@ old unemployed man be execute for carry out an assault on 32 people , mostly small children , at a kindergarten in eastern china in april .
the man , xu yuyuan , wield a knife usually use to slaughter pig .
xu , who be sentence to death on may 15 , tell the court his motive be to vent his rage against society after lose money gamble and in business dealing , and suffer setback in his personal life .
in late april , a former doctor who stab eight schoolchildren to death in a march school attack be execute .
two other school assailant have commit suicide .
premier wen jiabao say last month that long @-@ stand social concern include joblessness and a gape rich @-@ poor divide be partially to blame for the string of attack .
" we need to resolve the deep @-@ seat cause that have result in these problem , " wen say in an interview with hong kong @-@ based phoenix television .
" this include handle social contradiction , resolve dispute and strengthen mediation at the grassroots level ."
gadhafi attack us in speech in italy
rome 2009 @-@ 06 @-@ 11 13 @:@ 34 @:@ 38 utc
libyan leader moammar gadhafi on thursday urge the world to understand what motivate terrorist , and likened the 1986 u.s. strike on libya to osama bin laden 's terror attack .
gadhafi , who be long accuse of sponsor terrorism , get tepid applause from the italian lawmakers he address on the second day of a trip to italy , libya 's former colonial ruler .
" it be not very intelligent to chase terrorist down the afghan mountain or central asia , " gadhafi say in the hour @-@ long speech .
" that 's impossible .
we must look at their reason ."
he call for dialogue with terrorist , say , " one must talk to the devil , if it bring about a solution ."
sarcastically , he ask , " what 's the difference between the u.s. airstrikes on our home and bin laden 's action ? "
if anything , he say , bin laden be an outlaw , while the unite state be a country that should abide by international law .
former president ronald reagan order airstrikes on tripoli and benghazi in april 1986 after an attack on a disco in germany kill three people , include two u.s. servicemen .
the libyans say the retaliatory attack kill 41 people , include gadhafi 's adopt daughter , and injure 226 others .
the libyan leader tell the lawmakers he be be intentionally provocative " in order to try and understand act of terrorism ."
gadhafi have long be ostracize by the west for sponsor terrorism , but in recent year seek to emerge from his pariah status by abandon weapon of mass destruction and renounce terrorism in 2003 .
libya have since agree to pay compensation to the family of the berlin disco victim as well as the family of the victim of the 1988 pan am 103 bomb over lockerbie , scotland , which kill 270 people , include 189 americans .
libyan abdel basset ali al @-@ megrahi be convict of blow up the plane .
the unite state restore diplomatic tie with libya in 2006 and remove the north african nation from the state department list of country that sponsor terrorism .
gadhafi 's visit to italy continue that process of emergence from international isolation .
but it also draw protest , include at la sapienza university , where gadhafi be address a group of few hundred student .
the speech to lawmakers be likely to raise more controversy .
he have be set to speak inside the italian senate , a rare honor for visit dignitary .
but opposition lawmakers balk , forcing the speech to be move to a palazzo next door .
enrico morando , a senator of the opposition democratic party , say gadhafi 's presence at the senate would have be a " humiliation of this country 's democratic and republican spirit ."
" only those who have the credentials _ in term of democracy and protection of human right _ be entitle to speak to parliament , the inviolable temple of democracy , " he tell la repubblica newspaper .
human right organization and other critic have also denounce a recent deal that allow italy to send immigrant back to libya if they be intercept at sea .
they also decry libya 's treatment of the migrant and its poor human right record .
protest intensify in bolivia over gasoline price
la paz , bolivia 2010 @-@ 12 @-@ 31 01 @:@ 59 @:@ 04 utc
protest against a sharp increase in fuel price intensify and turn violent in bolivia on thursday , as thousand of demonstrator demand president evo morales ' government repeal the hike .
demonstrator fill the street in la paz and other city to protest the higher price , which be announce suddenly on sunday , prompt an immediate 73 percent jump in gasoline price and an 83 percent rise in price for diesel .
it also lead to rapid increase in transport and food price in the andean country .
some demand the resignation of morales , a close ally of venezuelan president hugo chavez .
it have be the most unpopular measure of morales ' five @-@ year presidency .
taxi driver hold a strike that largely paralyzed la paz on thursday , and protest be also hold in the city of cochabamba , santa cruz , potosi and oruro .
the march in the capital begin peacefully but clash with police erupt when demonstrator try to enter the main plaza where the government palace be locate .
police use tear gas to disperse the protester , who hurl stone at officer , the vice president 's office , a union headquarters and two ministry building .
in el alto , neighboring the capital , demonstrator set afire a car and toll booth .
people line a bridge while protester raise fist demand the measure be repeal .
interior minister sacha llorenti say disturbance in la paz , el alto and cochabamba leave 15 police officer injure , two seriously .
a group of protester burn a venezuelan flag .
" we make a call for calm , for tranquility ; there be police on patrol to guarantee security , " llorenti tell a news conference .
fuel price have be freeze for six year , but the government say it could no longer afford to subsidize them , especially since much be smuggle across the border to neighboring country .
respond to the protest , morales ' government have announce step aim at mitigate the economic effect _ include 20 percent salary increase for public worker aim at offset higher fuel price .
the government also announce new assistance to rice , corn and wheat farmer intend to increase production and bring down price .
demonstrator have call their protest the " gasolinazo ."
neighborhood protest leader claudio luna say in la paz that the government 's " message have n't meet the expectation of the population , and for that reason we 're go to continue the protest ."
he say demonstrator want price lower back to their former level .
bus driver have also hold sporadic protest this week , demand the government further increase fare .
authority order raise of 60 to 80 percent in public transport fare , but bus driver argue that be n't enough to offset the higher cost .
food price have also rise 15 percent in subsidized government market , but that remain much less than in private supermarket .
people seek bargain line up at a state @-@ run food store in la paz on thursday .
morales , meanwhile , say in a news conference that he be invite adviser from paraguay 's government to help formulate additional measure to lessen the blow of eliminate fuel subsidy .
