scott reject bar 's list
time @/@ herald tallahassee bureau
tallahassee — gov . rick scott , seek to bring the court system more in line with his conservative outlook , have repeatedly reject list recommend to him by the florida bar of lawyer seek to screen candidate for judgeships .
scott have reject dozen of attorney the bar have nominate to serve on judicial nominate commission , create decade ago to professionalize the bench and make merit and qualification at least as important as political connection .
''he want people with humility , '' say scott’s chief counsel , pete antonacci , ''and he want judge who will follow the law and not make it up as they go along.''
the bar say scott’s two predecessor , charlie crist and jeb bush , never reject any of its nominee .
all 26 nominate commission for the trial and appellate court and the supreme court be compose of nine member .
scott appoint five member of his choose and must appoint four others from list provide by the bar’s board of governor , some of whom be liberal democrat who do not support scott’s election .
the governor have reject the list 16 time and have never publicly give a reason and be not require to do so .
scott have send back so many bar @-@ recommend name that the group keep a five @-@ page spreadsheet to track them .
